contentrichtext.text: '''Bandon''' is the name of several places *[[Bandon, County Cork]], Ireland *the [[River Bandon]] in Ireland *[[Bandon (UK Parliament constituency)]], former constituency (1801-1885) in Ireland *Bandon, the old name of [[Surat Thani]] in Thailand **the [[Bandon Bay]] near Surat Thani *[[Bandon, Oregon]], USA '''Bandon''' may also refer to: *The [[Earl of Bandon]] *[[Bandon (Byzantine Empire)]], a Byzantine military and administrative unit {{Disambig}} [[Category:Place name disambiguation pages]]
